	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nova, quae apud nos sunt, ex d. <persName ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlino</persName> fusissime habes, qui ultro se obtulit velle ad te scribere, quae in <placeName type="auto_name">Saxonicis</placeName> civitatibus aguntur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus adiuvet fortes milites illos et spiritu fortitudinis donet, quo omnibus hostibus Christi resistant et ne modum per impęnitentem vitam excedant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Saxonum</persName> animi dubii sunt, et nescio, quo se vertant ob imminens periculum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mallent <persName type="auto_name">Mauritium</persName>; est ultra <persName type="auto_name">Caspios</persName> montes.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Videbimus domini iustum iudicium.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt <persName type="auto_name">Saxonem</persName> ducem veterem a <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinando</persName> rege invitatum et inter cętera mentionem fuisse de regis maiestate Romana, quam indeptus est <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandus</persName> per reliquos electores.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ad hęc dixit <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandus</persName>: "Her..., so ir mit mir hetten gholffen die chur k[uniglicher]<note type="margin">a.R.: (c)hen?</note> m[ajestät] bestetigen, so welte ich langist gluͦgt haben, das ir weren ledig von diser captivitet worden."</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid sibi hoc portendat, non ignoras absque dubio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legatus regis <placeName type="auto_name">Galliae</placeName> hodie ad nos venit; d. <persName ref="p944" cert="high">Maurus</persName> aliquid novi adportabit et pro <persName ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlino</persName> operam dabit, ne eiicietur homo dignus maiori honore.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 1550. 29. decembris.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Precor tibi et tuis felicissimum annum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="auto_name">G[astius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. Heinrycho Bullingero, Tigurinae ecclesiae pastori vigilantissimo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zurich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
